results.title: US Seller, free shipping, fast shipping, diamond painting kit, live love laugh, 30x30cm, round drill, full drill
results.description:
Welcome to your new favorite hobby! Incredibly relaxing and fun diamond painting kits. I am a US seller based in Charleston, SC and have done many of the kits myself. 

Similar to paint by number but using faceted resin “diamonds” (drills) that are pressed to a labeled sticky canvas.  All materials included to create your painting (labeled canvas, resin drills, applicator pen, wax for your pen, tray to hold drills).

I have listed designs that are beautiful to frame for your home or create and give as a gift. Frames are not included. The second picture in each listing gives an idea of how to display but are not true to size. These are measured in centimeters. 30cmx30cm is approximately 12 inches x 12 inches. 30cmx40cm is approximately 12 inches x 16 inches.

I do my best to send out orders the same day or the next day and ship USPS with a delivery time of 2-4 days. Get your kits fast. 

These are pixelated, so the larger the canvas, the more detail you will see. Full drill means that the diamonds will cover the entire canvas. Your canvas can be easily flattened by rolling the opposite way and placing under a heavy book overnight. 

I will inventory your drills before shipping to make sure you have all the colors and amounts of each needed to complete your painting. I will also enclose small ziplock bags to make it easier to store them. When you receive your kit you will be ready to unroll your canvas and get started. 

Have fun!
Leslie
